          <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-[#003087] leading-relaxed">
            For too long, patients have been left to navigate medical imaging on
            their own — unclear prices, long wait times, inconsistent equipment
            quality, and little to no transparency about who's reading their
            scans.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Right side with Problem illustration -->
        <div>
          <!-- Problem Illustration SVG -->
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            viewBox="0 0 600 300"
            class="w-full h-auto max-h-[80vh] object-cover rounded-xl shadow-2xl"
